commentText: Parse settings for a single client.
codeText: static Ec2ClientSettings getClientSettings(Settings settings) {_        final BasicAWSCredentials credentials = loadCredentials(settings)__        try (SecureString proxyUsername = PROXY_USERNAME_SETTING.get(settings)__             SecureString proxyPassword = PROXY_PASSWORD_SETTING.get(settings)) {_            return new Ec2ClientSettings(_                credentials,_                ENDPOINT_SETTING.get(settings),_                PROTOCOL_SETTING.get(settings),_                PROXY_HOST_SETTING.get(settings),_                PROXY_PORT_SETTING.get(settings),_                proxyUsername.toString(),_                proxyPassword.toString(),_                (int)READ_TIMEOUT_SETTING.get(settings).millis())__        }_    }
